ANNOUNCEMENTS (02): FREE GIDEON EBOOK, INFECTIOUS DISEASES OF VANUATU
********************************************************************
A ProMED-mail post
http://www.promedmail.org
ProMED-mail is a program of the
International Society for Infectious Diseases
http://www.isid.org

Date: 28 Mar 2015
From: Uri Blackman <uri@GIDEONonline.com> [edited]


Following the Typhoon Hainan disaster, ProMED and GIDEON Informatics released over 1000 free copies of an eBook, Infectious Diseases of the Philippines, to concerned Health Care Workers, Military Personnel, Humanitarian Aid workers and ProMED subscribers. In response to the devastation and suffering which have now struck Vanuatu, we have arranged to distribute free copies of Infectious Diseases of Vanuatu, 2015: 356 pages, 42 graphs, 1476 linked references. http://www.gideononline.com/ebooks/country/infectious-diseases-of-vanuatu

This offer will also include a 25 percent discount on all other titles in their eBook series. The publisher has arranged to donate a percentage of sales to ProMED.

Infectious Diseases of Vanuatu, 2015 is one of 423 e-books which follow the field of Geographic Medicine http://www.gideononline.com/ebooks, overall containing 120 000 pages, 35 000 graphs, and 435 000 linked references. The series includes a comprehensive book covering the infectious diseases of your own country / every individual disease. Additional volumes are dedicated to all bacteria, yeasts, anti-infective drugs and vaccines. The entire series is updated yearly.

To access your free copy of Infectious Diseases of Vanuatu, 2015:
- Click on http://www.gideononline.com/ebooks/country/infectious-diseases-of-vanuatu
- Click Add coupon
- Enter promed
- Complete Checkout
- Click link in separate email to download the eBook

For additional eBooks at 25 percent discount:
- Access list of titles at http://www.gideononline.com/ebooks
- Use coupon 25promed to checkout

